00:03:16.730 --> 00:03:18.649
-Što?
-Dobro si se naspavao?

00:03:18.691 --> 00:03:21.569
Zbilja si se svidio onim striptizetama sinoć.

00:03:21.652 --> 00:03:23.279
O čemu ti to?

00:03:23.362 --> 00:03:24.905
